  <p>
    West Coast Seeds becomes more useful when your environment limits how quickly crops can grow.
  </p>

  <p>
    It works best for:
  </p>

  <ul class="plainList">
    <li>cooler climates with lower heat accumulation</li>
    <li>shorter growing seasons</li>
